Wasu 'yan majalisar sun yi tir da shawarar da aka yi na a sauya musu lakabi zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
An yi gargadi ne bayan da aka ce Majalisar ta fi dacewa a kira ta Welsh Parliament.
Yanzu 'yan majalisa daga bangarori daban-daban na siyasa suna tsoron sabon mukamin zai sa su zama abin dariya.
Wani dan majalisar na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce jam'iyyarsa ta damu cewa sabon sunan zai yi amfani da kalmomin Twp da Pwp.
Amma ga masu karatu da suke yaren Welsh, a yaren Welsh, twp yana nufin abu ɗaya, kuma pwp yana nufin abu ɗaya.
Wani daga cikin 'yan jam'iyyar Plaid ya ce duk rukunin jam'iyyar ba su ji daɗi ba, kuma suna ba da shawara a madadin.
Wani dan majalisar mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce jam'iyyarsa a bude take ga sauya sunan, amma ya ce yanzu juyin mulki daga MWP zuwa 'Muppet' ya yi nisa.
A nan yana da kyau a lura cewa a cikin harshen Welsh ana furta harafin w kamar yadda ake furta u a cikin Yorkshire English, wato MWP da map.
Matsayin kwamitin majalisar da ke da alhakin tsara dokar da za ta sauya sunan shi ne kamar haka: Yanayin karshe game da sunayen da za a yi wa mambobin majalisar dokokin na hannun 'yan majalisar.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba da damar Majalisar Welsh ta canza suna.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta fitar da sakamakon binciken da aka yi na jama'a, wanda ya ba da shawarar saka sunan Majalisar Wales, wanda ya samu goyon baya mai yawa.
Dangane da taken MLA, Hukumar ta fi son taken Welsh Parliament Member da WMP, amma a cikin tattaunawar da aka yi da jama'a an fi son MWP.
'Yan majalisar sun ci gaba da gabatar da sabbin dabaru, amma samun yarjejeniya yana da matukar wahala, wanda ke haifar da matsala ga shugaban majalisar, Elin Jones, wanda dole ne ya gabatar da kudirin doka game da canjin sunaye a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
Dokar da ta shafi sake fasalin za ta shafi ayyukan majalisar dokokin ta wasu bangarori, da suka hada da hana 'yan majalisar wakilai daga yin aiki da tsarin kwamitocin.
