Ya yi wannan magana ne bayan da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi sanarwa game da kirkirar basirar mutum, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar kirkirar mutum.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta sanar da wani shiri na musamman: burinta na zama babbar mai samar da AI a duniya nan da shekarar 2030.
"Raba na'urar AI da aka tanada zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, saboda duk sauran kasashen duniya sun yi baya a kan Amurka, kuma wata babbar nasara ta AI tana nan tafe", in ji Lee.
Ta hanyar ninka tallafin da ake ba da wa bincike, za a ninka damar da Amurka ke da ita na samun ci gaba a fannin ilimin kere kere, kamar yadda ya bayyana a wata hira da aka yi da shi a CNBC.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order ya fito ne a wannan watan a hannun Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a Face++, wani kamfani na AI a China.
A cikin shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin AI wanda ya ci nasara a kan mafi kyawun ɗan wasan Amurka Othello, kuma daga baya ya yi aiki a matsayin memba na Microsoft Research da shugaban reshen Google na China.
Lee ya yaba wa sakamakon da gwamnatin Amurka ta samu a gasar fasaha da ta gabata, ciki har da DARPA Robotics Challenge, kuma ya yi tambaya game da lokacin da za a sake gudanar da irin wannan gasar domin a lokacin ne za a iya samun damar gano sabbin masu tsara makomar.
Masu bincike a Amurka sukan yi aiki tuƙuru don samun tallafin gwamnati, in ji Lee.
"Ba kasar Sin ba ce ke jan ragamar masana kimiyya, manyan kamfanoni ne ke janye ta".
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha a cikin 'yan shekarun nan sun yi kwangilar da manyan jami'o'i don yin aiki a fannin AI.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen da aka yi a kan shige-shige zai taimaka sosai ga kokarin da Amurka ke yi a fannin fasahar kere-kere.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba wa waɗanda ke da digiri na biyu a fannin ilimin kere kere katin zama mai zaman kansa", in ji shi.
A watan Yulin 2017, kwamitin kula da harkokin gwamnati na kasar Sin ya sanar da shirinsa na bunkasa fasahar kere kere ta zamani.
Gidauniyar kimiyya ta kasar Sin tana ba da tallafi ga ma'aikatan cibiyoyin ilimi kamar yadda Asusun Kimiyya na Kasa (NSF) da sauran hukumomin gwamnati ke ba da kuɗi ga masu bincike na Amurka, amma ingancin aikin ilimi a China ya yi ƙasa, in ji Lee.
